text: Gannett is an unincorporated community in Blaine County in the U.S. state of Idaho. Gannett is located 8 mi (12.9 km) southeast of Bellevue on Gannett Road between State Highway 75 and U.S. Route 20. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Blaine County, Idaho Category:Unincorporated communities in Idaho
